{"tid":517025,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［實至名歸？］李克勤 ： 年紀大，應該要敬老。","createTime":"2018-01-02T02:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T03:05:15.000Z","uid":49388,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1f446e72657b5ca5d8cff9a9ae3f3911fd8ee5e7","tid":517025,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:23:23.000Z","msg":"仲有無連登仔話佢實至名歸？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180101/57652954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180101%2F57652954&d=ZGLzGSuEDofInY%2FLzkwlTDANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=1383d43c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180101%2F57652954&h=5d923aad\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180101/57652954</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180101/large/1514813140_80bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180101%2Flarge%2F1514813140_80bd.jpg&h=0be4e564&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n李克勤今年「回歸香港樂壇」，挾三首冠軍歌成為叱咤男歌手大熱，對手包括側田陳柏宇等等，《失魂記》仲殺入我最喜愛歌曲五強。方才克勤接受商台訪問拉票時，繼續妙語如珠，謂希望大家投《失魂記》一票，「希望大家失魂嘅時候投《失魂記》一票啦。」又自嘲：「年紀大，應該要敬老嘅。」講到話今年好勤力，克勤又嚟料：「勤力係因為要跑數，因為我簽咗呢間公司（英皇），合約其中一部份係要跑數，唔係追唔番條數。」<br />\n<br />\n講完笑，克勤再謂：「講真，其實個個歌手都勤力，我諗今晚坐得喺度嘅個個都勤力，唔止係我，睇下邊個好彩。」去年由年頭忙到年尾，今年會否休息一下，陪多啲家人？佢即話：「唔會啦！我啲仔都大喇！」但預告今年會做多啲國語歌。<br />\n<br />\n之前克勤喺港台同勁歌頒獎禮都好多「弦外之音」，今次又再抽自己水嗌「敬老」，睇佢表情都&hellip;有啲硬&hellip;"},{"pid":"b603ad2e87a6ab303fe6c91328aeaf8e25f4fe43","tid":517025,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:25:28.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦國語歌"},{"pid":"bf260e6904bc0208862cd898094874080e14ca2f","tid":517025,"uid":26451,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:26:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc5a985a5123f33206979937468e90fa07efcee5","tid":517025,"uid":40662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T02:42:32.000Z","msg":"又係嗰啲用廣東腔唱嘅國語歌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f862358676bc4297fedb26b3d2f81b582dd5855","tid":517025,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T03:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ba4fee8d6c54aef60eee59eadcb93c7faac177","tid":517025,"uid":70391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T03:52:55.000Z","msg":"係努力既佢"},{"pid":"7861569422e3611e0a46da942fe03d640979abf6","tid":517025,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T02:46:26.000Z","msg":"個樣衰咗好多"},{"pid":"b16a07664daaeb33f9ae204c0ca306da3e2a8d9a","tid":517025,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7bc49cea9a57afd3268c410c211b8f29dfd6ecb","tid":517025,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f7e6ca87210cbe2d3f683540ef4b30bda7b4815","tid":517025,"uid":128219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}